                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Uncertainties in the measured cross-section",
                "values are due predominantly to the target thickness",
                "uncertainty of 8.9%. Errors due to statistical",
                "fluctuations, efficiency variations, and to the",
                "calculation of the correction factor for absorption",
                "in the tantalum are each of the order of 2% or less.",
                "The combined error is 9.1 or 9.2% in most yield",
                "determinations."
              ]
            },
